name: extreme_if_branchwise_compare_gte
section: control-if-comparison
args: cond:Bool a:Int b:Int c:Int d:Int
type: Bool
expect: True
description: Branchwise comparison >= under the same condition must select the correct comparison.
law: (= (>= (if {cond} {a} {b}) (if {cond} {c} {d})) (if {cond} (>= {a} {c}) (>= {b} {d})))
